et brioche<\/strong>: increase sugar to 130 g and divide dough into 12 equal pieces. Shape portions into buns, then place onto prepared baking tray and bake for 20 minutes (200°C)."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 50m","12 portions"]}